<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110594-0039 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 095410 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 5, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
