<HEADLINE>
<P>
4 NIGERIANS BEHEADED FOR MURDER IN MECCA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Four Nigerians convicted of murdering a woman whose home they broke into were 
beheaded Friday in Mecca, the Interior Ministry announced. 
</P>
<P>
 Nearly 50 convicted murderers, rapists and drug traffickers have been beheaded 
under Islamic law, or Sharia, this year, usually in public squares after 
Friday's Muslim Sabbath prayers. 
</P>
</TEXT>
