<P>
 United Paramount Network Names Entertainment Chief: Michael Sullivan, a former 
ABC executive, will be president of entertainment for the television network 
that is to be launched in January.Sullivan will direct all areas of 
entertainment programming. As an independent producer, he developed the sitcom 
"Growing Pains" in conjunction with Warner Bros. Television. United Paramount 
is owned by Viacom Inc.'s Paramount Television and a subsidiary of Chris-Craft 
Industries. 
