<P>
PRO FOOTBALL / DAILY REPORT; RAMS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By T.J. SIMERS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Baltimore Oriole owner Peter Angelos, scheduled to meet Ram President John 
Shaw in Los Angeles on Friday, had to postpone his trip "because some business 
came up in Baltimore." Angelos, who wants to purchase a minority interest in 
the Rams and move them to Baltimore, has rescheduled the meeting for next week. 
T.J. SIMERS 
</P>
